      <data key="d8">INHALATION VOLUME OF CO2 RELATIVE TO THE VOLUME EMITTED</data>
      <data key="d9">REDUCES</data>
      <data key="d10">Opening windows, by increasing ventilation, reduces the relative inhalation volume of CO2 at various positions in the bus, indicating lower exposure to rebreathed air.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.8</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">e45568c3-e22e-4830-92f5-64de955e8aee_chunk_4</data>
