      <data key="d8">VENTILATION FAN OPERATION</data>
      <data key="d9">COMPLEMENTS</data>
      <data key="d10">Window opening and ventilation fan operation can be used together to enhance overall ventilation in the bus cabin, providing greater air exchange and dilution than either measure alone.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.7</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">e45568c3-e22e-4830-92f5-64de955e8aee_chunk_4</data>
