      <data key="d8">ACH IN THE BUS</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DOSE</data>
      <data key="d10">The configuration with the right front and left rear windows open produces a specific ACH profile in the bus, reflecting cross-ventilation between front and rear. | The configuration with the right front and right rear windows open yields a distinct ACH in the bus, shaping longitudinal airflow along the right side. | The configuration with the right rear and left rear windows open determines a particular ACH in the bus, emphasizing ventilation in the rear cabin.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.8</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">e45568c3-e22e-4830-92f5-64de955e8aee_chunk_4</data>
      <data key="d14">e45568c3-e22e-4830-92f5-64de955e8aee</data>
